## About Marcus Spanier

**Frontend / Backend / WordPress Engineer**

I’m Marcus, a seasoned WordPress developer with over 15 years of experience in frontend and backend development. I specialize in custom plugin and theme development, API integrations, and WooCommerce extensions for B2B and e-commerce solutions. My focus is on performance, maintainability, and delivering scalable, user-friendly solutions.

Currently, I’m part of the team at AdSuits, contributing to modern WordPress development with a strong technical foundation.